也是计划今年要小孩，但是迫于现在的经济压力，还有现实情况，真的不敢生。 老公也是报喜不报忧，几乎从毕业后，就再也没有接受家里的帮助，但是他现在也没什么钱，他爸爸在老家做一些工程承包，还是有一定定的收入，我和老公结婚，他家里是没有给彩礼的，我老公自己转了小几万给我做彩礼。现在家婆几乎每个星期都打电话，旁敲侧击的催生，言语里还是强调让我妈妈来帮忙，不想出钱也不想出力，心眼完全偏到家里小儿子小女儿去了，加之最近和老公也有矛盾，让我真的很生气。 最后感慨一下，真的不能嫁家里有两个男孩的，特别是还偏心另外一个小孩的。"},"attached_info":"CkAImYndo+uotoULEAMaCTEwODQxNzgzMSC1p9+yBjAAOPMBQCVyCTY1NzYzMDAyOXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"38 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"38_1717319893.169584","card_id":"Q_653640316","target":{"id":653640316,"title":"为什么沙俄可以在短短60年间占领整个西伯利亚，而明朝却无法做到？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/653640316","type":"question","created":1713680379,"answer_count":204,"follower_count":536,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[248,5925,13519,118627,172983],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"1580年到1640俄国在短短60年期间席卷了西起乌拉尔山，东到堪察加半岛的广大区域。而相对距离更近的大明取从未染指该地区。是什么客观原因影响了中原向该地区的力量投射？（北京和莫斯科到托木斯克的直线距离差不多）"},"attached_info":"CkAImYndo+uotoULEAMaCTEwNzUzMTI3NSD735KxBjAAOJgEQCZyCTY1MzY0MDMxNngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"37 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ac22711c7e7d55ccc0bc3a23b4e55140_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"39_1717319893.170374","card_id":"Q_636442892","target":{"id":636442892,"title":"如何评价Mygo!!!!!这个乐队？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/636442892","type":"question","created":1703429258,"answer_count":28,"follower_count":109,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[718,199453],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"不谈动画，主要谈乐队本身和歌以及成员"},"attached_info":"Cj8ImYndo+uotoULEAMaCTEwMzcxMDE0OSCKiaGsBjAAOG1AJ3IJNjM2NDQ